Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.50,0:01:10.59,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}放課後　下駄箱　響く雨音
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.34,0:01:16.47,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}傘なく駆け出す　シャツが濡れる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.14,0:01:22.31,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}大人のあなたに届かなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.97,0:01:28.31,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}たやすく触れてる雨に　雨になりたい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.15,0:01:33.07,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}触れさせて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.86,0:01:43.45,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}1、子ども扱いしないでください
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.70,0:01:49.33,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}2、優しくして、ごまかすのはもっとダメ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.42,0:01:52.42,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}好きなんです　（聞こえてる？）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.42,0:01:54.84,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}好きなんです
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.21,0:02:00.05,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}水たまり　今は飛び越えられるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.18,0:02:06.77,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}雨上がり虹がかかって　やっと目が合った
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.77,0:02:11.77,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}恋に鈍感なあなた　だから
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.73,0:02:18.36,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}夏の青さに　水滴がキラリ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.36,0:02:25.45,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}ルルララ恋をしてる　雨上がりに
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.50,0:02:33.54,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}この瞬間迷わない　傘はいらない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.50,0:01:10.59,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}放学铃响  走向鞋箱  雨欢闹正忙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.34,0:01:16.47,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}抛开雨伞  纵情嬉玩  沾湿了衣衫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.14,0:01:22.31,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}成熟的你  青涩的我  距离太遥远
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.97,0:01:28.31,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}好想变成那满天的雨滴  这样就能触摸到你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.15,0:01:33.07,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}让我触摸你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.86,0:01:43.45,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}第一、不要随随便便把我当成小女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.70,0:01:49.33,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}第二、对我温柔一点  更加不能撒谎把我哄骗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.42,0:01:52.42,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}就是喜欢你（你听得到吗?）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.42,0:01:54.84,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}就是喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.21,0:02:00.05,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}浅浅的水洼  看我一下子就跳过它
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.18,0:02:06.77,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}雨后晴天里彩虹露出了笑脸  终于和你对上了眼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.77,0:02:11.77,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}谁让你对爱太迟钝  没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.73,0:02:18.36,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}夏日里  蓝天下  水滴闪闪发光
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.36,0:02:25.45,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}噜噜啦啦  和爱不期而遇  就在雨过天晴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.50,0:02:33.54,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur3}这一瞬间  没有犹豫  放开雨伞拥抱爱情
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Comment,,0,0,0,,——ED——
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.84,0:21:23.55,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Raining　夏の午後に
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.84,0:21:26.72,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}通り雨　傘の下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.97,0:21:29.80,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Kissing　濡れた頬に
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.97,0:21:33.93,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}そっと口づけた
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.93,0:21:41.82,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}あの季節にまだ焦がれている
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.28,0:21:50.20,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}何も手につかずに　上の空の日々
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.49,0:21:55.16,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Nothing but you're the part of me
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.46,0:22:01.29,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}まだ足りなくて　まだ消えなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.63,0:22:07.63,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}重ねた手のひらから幼さが
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.72,0:22:10.55,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}What a good thing we lose
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.85,0:22:13.64,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}What a bad thing we knew
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.85,0:22:19.73,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}そんなフレーズに濡れてく雨の中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.02,0:22:25.94,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}ただ足りなくて　まだ言えなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.19,0:22:32.12,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}数えた日の夢からさよならが
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.37,0:22:35.29,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}What a good thing we lose
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.41,0:22:38.33,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}What a bad thing we knew
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.54,0:22:46.46,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}触れられずにいれたら　笑えたかな？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.84,0:21:23.55,EDCN-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Raining  夏日的午后
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.84,0:21:26.72,EDCN-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}雨来了又去  留我在伞下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.97,0:21:29.80,EDCN-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Kissing  沾湿的脸颊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.97,0:21:33.93,EDCN-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}轻轻一吻  现了红霞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.93,0:21:41.82,EDCN-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}四季更了又替  不变的是焦急的心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.28,0:21:50.20,EDCN-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}我无心做任何事情  心中想的一直是你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.49,0:21:55.16,EDCN-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Nothing but you're the part of me
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.46,0:22:01.29,EDCN-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}还想再索取一点  还感觉隐隐若现
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.63,0:22:07.63,EDCN-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}十指相扣  掌心微热  是你青涩的炽烈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.72,0:22:10.55,EDCN-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}What a good thing we lose
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.85,0:22:13.64,EDCN-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}What a bad thing we knew
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.85,0:22:19.73,EDCN-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}一字一句沁我心  像身旁飘落的雨点
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.02,0:22:25.94,EDCN-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}只想再索取一点  告别梗在了嘴边
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.19,0:22:32.12,EDCN-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}细数曾经满怀憧憬追逐梦想的当年
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.37,0:22:35.29,EDCN-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}What a good thing we lose
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.41,0:22:38.33,EDCN-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}What a bad thing we knew
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.54,0:22:46.46,EDCN-CHS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}如果不能伸手触摸  是否还能保持笑脸?
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Comment,,0,0,0,,——Title——
Comment: 0,0:02:35.21,0:02:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,愁雨
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Comment,,0,0,0,,——Text——
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.29,0:00:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.42,0:00:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,让…让你久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.51,0:00:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 准备花了些时间
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.22,0:00:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.97,0:00:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,喂!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.89,0:00:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,小晶!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.10,0:00:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 她们就是要跟着来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.74,0:00:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.16,0:00:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.22,0:02:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,真厉害 是鱼!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.88,0:02:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,是鱼!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.59,0:02:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,瞧一瞧看一看!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.47,0:02:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,一串一律300日元
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.18,0:02:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,给我来串蜜柑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.31,0:02:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,好嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.06,0:02:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,小翔好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.48,0:02:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,长高了不少啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.40,0:02:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,算是吧 青春期嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.90,0:02:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我要章鱼烧!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.36,0:02:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,还有我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.28,0:03:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,好好好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.36,0:03:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.57,0:03:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,注意衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.62,0:03:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,不过上次我在书店看见你了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.33,0:03:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.12,0:03:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,看你和朋友在一起 所以就没打招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.29,0:03:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,这有什么好介意的 打招呼呗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.50,0:03:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,怕打扰你嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.21,0:03:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,遥姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.88,0:03:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,尿尿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.88,0:03:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,尿尿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.97,0:03:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,啊? 现在想尿?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.14,0:03:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我带她们去?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.89,0:03:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,能拜托你吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.77,0:03:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,作为交换你得支付500日元
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.48,0:03:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.65,0:03:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢惠顾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.36,0:03:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,来 我们走
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.57,0:03:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,尿尿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.61,0:03:37.65,Comment,,0,0,0,,快一点!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.73,0:03:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的 蹬鼻子上脸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.40,0:03:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正粗圆_GBK\bord0\fs55\fax0.2\c&H28486B&\frz343.9\pos(546.667,260.666)}钓悠悠
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.40,0:03:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正粗圆_GBK\bord0\fs45\fax0.2\c&H2F5A86&\frz343.6\pos(538.667,403.333)}※必得一个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.40,0:03:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正粗圆_GBK\bord0\fs45\fax0.2\c&H2F5A86&\pos(526.667,587.333)\frz344.5}1次                           200日元
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.15,0:03:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我来一次
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.32,0:03:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,200日元
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.91,0:03:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.87,0:03:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,大叔 我也来一次
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.33,0:03:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,200日元
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.83,0:03:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,给 用这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.12,0:03:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,真令人怀念
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.88,0:03:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,晶 你想要哪个?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.38,0:03:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我要个红的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.96,0:03:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,红的啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.89,0:04:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我也要红的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.56,0:04:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我怎么感觉那钓线一年比一年脆?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.82,0:04:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,有什么关系
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.94,0:04:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,反正必得一个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.65,0:04:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,去那边休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.95,0:04:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,晶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.91,0:04:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你今天邀请我来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.16,0:04:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我离开社团之后 我们第一次出来玩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.64,0:04:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,结果大家都没能通过预选
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.48,0:04:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,很丢人 对吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.02,0:05:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,石井她也很不甘心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.15,0:05:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么会丢人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.79,0:05:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我说 晶…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.70,0:05:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你偶尔也回来社团…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.97,0:05:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 等我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.47,0:05:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,晶?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.27,0:05:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,这是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.89,0:05:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,也不是她父亲啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.40,0:05:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 是我打工的店里的店长
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.07,0:05:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,店长…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.54,0:05:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,晶…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.58,0:05:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你喜欢他?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.21,0:05:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.00,0:06:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,不会吧! 这大叔一个啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.55,0:06:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,而且身边那个男孩是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.39,0:06:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,好了别说了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.43,0:06:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,去找翔他们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.60,0:06:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,晶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.77,0:06:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,晶 你最近有心事也不告诉我了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.61,0:06:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道你在想什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.03,0:06:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,你不也一样不问我吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.99,0:06:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你让我怎么开口!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.37,0:06:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,嘴上让我找你说话 让我问你的心事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.08,0:06:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,可你的一举一动都在阻止我这么做啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.59,0:06:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.22,0:06:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,喂! 你们哭什么啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.39,0:06:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.14,0:07:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我们已经回不到从前
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.90,0:07:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,好了好了 别哭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.78,0:07:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,遥?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.54,0:07:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.33,0:07:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,喂!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.62,0:07:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 神轿马上就要出发了!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.38,0:07:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,小晶 抱歉 我得走了!
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,（吆喝声）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.33,0:07:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,还是马场的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.63,0:08:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.55,0:08:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,这时候关门也未免太早了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.76,0:08:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 虽然有些早 先去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.07,0:08:34.70,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\an7}动点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.07,0:08:34.70,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fs32\an9}注：どんでん的音译。或源于「どんでん返し」 取「变化、逆转」之意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.70,0:08:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.08,0:08:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,没事 我才该道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.29,0:08:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.92,0:08:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.92,0:08:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,作者签名书!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.92,0:08:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,真幸运!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.30,0:08:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎光临!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.84,0:08:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,那个…我来见我朋友…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.97,0:09:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,在里边呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.40,0:09:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,千寻
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.94,0:09:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.07,0:09:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么偏偏选了这家店?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.66,0:09:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我们俩见面 能不选这里吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.70,0:09:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,真令人怀念
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.95,0:09:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,老板! 来瓶啤酒!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.29,0:09:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,好的!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.92,0:09:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.25,0:09:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,停 下酒菜我先点好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.46,0:09:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.25,0:09:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,让您久等了!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.59,0:09:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.55,0:09:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,没错 就是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.64,0:09:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,动点的味噌烤串豆腐!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.31,0:09:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我们俩见面 怎么能没有它呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.78,0:09:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,没想到你还会来联系我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.03,0:09:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,差不多…十年了吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.49,0:10:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,一切还好吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.87,0:10:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,算是吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.58,0:10:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,某个机会让我突然想起了你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.33,0:10:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你还是这么精神
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.92,0:10:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,那是自然
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.55,0:10:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,刚才我在店门前 看到有几个小女生拿着你的书呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.22,0:10:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你可能不太感兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.64,0:10:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,但还是有很多小女生喜欢我的书啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.35,0:10:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,确实还算有意思吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.06,0:10:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你…你看过了?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.44,0:10:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,看过了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.31,0:10:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你特意买了?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.73,0:10:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.48,0:10:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.40,0:10:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,图书馆借的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.53,0:10:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,好…好看吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.33,0:10:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,不是说了还行吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.62,0:10:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,「还行」是什么意思?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.00,0:10:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,非常好看才对吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.96,0:10:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,也就这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.29,0:10:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,那亚马逊上给一星评价的人是你了?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.25,0:10:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,那不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.51,0:10:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧算了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.63,0:11:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,今天久别重聚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.55,0:11:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我带了好东西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.81,0:11:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,看!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.10,0:11:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我们大学时代制作的同人志
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.65,0:11:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,真令人怀念!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.23,0:11:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,没错吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.65,0:11:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你居然还留着它
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.61,0:11:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.94,0:11:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你这「来白菜地里抓我呀」是什么怪标题?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.53,0:11:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,这时候缺钱 天天吃白菜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.83,0:11:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 高田学长
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.66,0:11:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我从前经常因为跟他争执影评而被揍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.50,0:11:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.21,0:11:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正准雅宋_GBK\fs60\bord0\c&H647A8C&\b1\frz335.4\pos(654.667,328.667)}翠
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.34,0:11:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 小翠?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.42,0:11:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你离婚几年了?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.34,0:11:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你俩现在还见面吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.72,0:11:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,没见
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.10,0:11:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,有时候在电话里谈谈儿子的事情而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.85,0:11:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,说好去印度玩的 你小子放我鸽子跑去结婚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.10,0:11:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,而我却在异乡的孤独中写成了出道小说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.28,0:12:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,当时是我对不起你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.25,0:12:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,都是青春啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.42,0:12:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你现在也在写吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.59,0:12:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.67,0:12:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,没 现在不写了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.63,0:12:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,骗人吧你 你这张脸哪里像不写小说了?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.76,0:12:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧…偶尔…有时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.85,0:12:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,稍微写两笔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.98,0:12:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,四五年没有写完整的故事了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.90,0:12:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,也不打算给别人看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.44,0:12:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,实在微不足道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.57,0:12:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经很久没有提起这事了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.58,0:12:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我身边也没有人知道我在偷偷写小说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.50,0:13:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,这也不是什么在人前炫耀的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.68,0:13:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.39,0:13:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,而且 想说的话 找我不就行了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.94,0:13:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,来 喝!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.11,0:13:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,老板! 再来一瓶啤酒!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.94,0:13:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,好嘞!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.45,0:13:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,毕竟都成大叔了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.75,0:13:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,物美! 价廉! 嘈杂!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.38,0:13:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,那家店简直就是学生的伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.21,0:13:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我喝得有些多
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.72,0:13:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,出租车来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.88,0:13:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,近藤 我带你一程
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.80,0:13:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,不了 我走走 醒酒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.47,0:13:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,什么? 走什么走上车啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.89,0:13:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我走路
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.68,0:13:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,上车
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.77,0:13:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,走路
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.48,0:13:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,那我也走路
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.06,0:14:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.62,0:14:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,不走了 走不动了!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.24,0:14:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,不是让你搭出租车了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.34,0:14:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.46,0:14:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你其实还在写吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.92,0:14:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么还问 都已经第十八遍了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.18,0:14:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,错! 正确答案是第十五遍
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.30,0:14:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,管它多少遍!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.52,0:14:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,不要紧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.44,0:14:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,骗你的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.15,0:14:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,近藤
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.86,0:14:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正隶变_GBK\fs40\bord1\be2\b1\fscy113\fscx100\3c&H000000&\pos(640,721)}快看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.95,0:14:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正隶变_GBK\fs40\bord1\be2\b1\fscy113\fscx100\3c&H000000&\pos(640,721)}月亮…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.41,0:14:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,无论远或近
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.79,0:15:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,不问清与浊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.21,0:15:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,但见玲珑月
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.63,0:15:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,影必现其中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.22,0:15:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,酸死了酸死了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.56,0:15:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,受不了受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.48,0:15:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我还是上出租车吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.15,0:15:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 上吧上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.78,0:15:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你还是用走的吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.49,0:15:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.24,0:15:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,车站不远了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.12,0:15:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你个老顽固
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.74,0:15:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,说起来 千寻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.08,0:15:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你小说里对那个高中生女主角的描写实在一般
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.13,0:15:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.21,0:15:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你又懂什么是JK?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.13,0:15:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你可别小看家庭餐厅店长!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.34,0:15:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.39,0:15:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,司机先生 开车
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.02,0:15:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.97,0:16:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,唉 还闹起别扭了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.10,0:16:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,真是孩子气
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.02,0:16:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不是大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.28,0:16:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,是同级生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.11,0:16:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,随时再联络!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.41,0:16:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,走了!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.13,0:16:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,走 去下一场!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.22,0:16:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,继续喝起来!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.88,0:16:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,知道了知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.76,0:16:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我是天才!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.22,0:16:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,全世界 看着吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.72,0:16:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,近藤 你稿子怎么还是手写的?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.52,0:16:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.10,0:16:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,不论过了多久 我都只想回到当年
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.94,0:16:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,回到那段跃动的青葱岁月
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.57,0:16:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,感受一同在胸膛里流动的热血
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.12,0:17:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,晶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.92,0:17:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.33,0:17:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.42,0:17:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,新学期了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.25,0:17:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我给你们捎了礼物!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.75,0:17:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,真的?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.46,0:17:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你去哪里了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.26,0:17:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,听我说话还不知道吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.01,0:17:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你这么说我也不明白啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.76,0:17:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道 是去了名古屋吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.14,0:17:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,喜屋武怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.10,0:17:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,去厕所?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.86,0:17:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,加一份薯条和炸鸡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.61,0:17:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.61,0:17:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.00,0:17:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉她没精打采的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.25,0:17:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,是因为西田今天不上班?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.05,0:17:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,上次那味噌烤豆腐串太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.72,0:18:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 您辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.64,0:18:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,辛苦了 需要帮忙吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.93,0:18:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,不了 我没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.24,0:18:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我看你今天没精打采的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.37,0:18:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,出什么事了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.16,0:18:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我和朋友吵架了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.67,0:18:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我们一直都一起在社团里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.50,0:18:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,但后来我不得不离开 彼此就变得尴尬了起来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.22,0:18:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,所以就…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.84,0:18:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,社团?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.01,0:18:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.93,0:18:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我们或许没法再和好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.69,0:18:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.02,0:18:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,橘!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.90,0:18:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 我回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.78,0:18:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.20,0:19:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,咦 今天晚上…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.08,0:19:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,橘 你来一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.67,0:19:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,您辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.84,0:19:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.81,0:19:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,是满月
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.52,0:19:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,不错
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.61,0:19:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,而且今晚的月亮是超级月亮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.32,0:19:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,超级月亮?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.98,0:19:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,比寻常的满月看上去更大更亮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.49,0:19:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,似乎还是实现愿望的预兆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.29,0:19:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,愿望…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.87,0:19:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我在学生时代
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.83,0:19:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,也在社团里有个好友
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.46,0:19:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然算不得大吵大闹
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.92,0:20:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,但终究还是变得尴尬 和他逐渐疏远了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.64,0:20:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你们的关系最后怎么样了?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.51,0:20:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,时隔十年 我们最近见了一面
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.64,0:20:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我真的很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.23,0:20:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我想自己会觉得高兴 应该是因为已经成了大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.32,0:20:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,但临别前 他说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.07,0:20:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,「我们不是大人」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.36,0:20:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,「是同级生」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.24,0:20:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,至于我想说的呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.54,0:20:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,就算你和你朋友现在分开了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.51,0:20:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,一起度过的那段宝贵的时间一定还在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.89,0:20:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,不论时光如何流逝 也绝不会消失
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.60,0:20:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,对你而言如此
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.94,0:20:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,对你朋友而言亦然
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.32,0:21:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,即便现在担心要擦肩而过
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.33,0:21:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,也要相信圆满的日子会再有
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.45,0:21:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,寄愿于这满月吧
Comment: 0,0:20:24.20,0:20:26.20,Comment,,0,0,0,,
